My daughter and I can not say enough about the top notch service we received. We were able to have dinner at the club as reciprocal members and they treated us as one of their own. The dinner was great and all of the staff were amazing but Taylor went out of her way to make me her new fall sangria which was delicious!! We will definitely be going back!!

The Center Club is a beautiful, private club in the heart of Baltimore, catering to high-end clientele.  They are 5 star in every area!  Professionalism, warm and welcoming hospitality, fine dining, exceptional service, events, views of the harbor... The Center Club has it all including Reza.  Reza is the most friendly, upscale, polite and wonderful waiter I've ever met, providing exemplary service and a smile with every interaction.
Outstanding private club offering a variety of services. Diverse membership. Many are high-level executives. The kitchen is fabulous and service is excellent. Free indoor parking in the evenings.
The center club continues to be one of the best places in Baltimore to do a business drink, dinner, or lunch. I love this place
